==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loathsome
<hw>Loath"some</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fitted to cause
loathing; exciting disgust; disgusting; <as>as, a <ex>loathsome</ex>
disease</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The most <qex>loathsome</qex> and deadly forms of infection.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Loath"some*ly</wf>. <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Loath"some*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loathy</ent>⟦br⟧
